    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Company for an Only Child, and for Parents, Peace of Mind'' (news article, June 3):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Company for an Only Child, and for Parents, Peace of Mind'' (news article, June 3):</p>
        <p>As the parent of a single child, I never mind being asked if there are or will be any others. I always answer: ''No. We got it right the first time.''</p>
        <p>Raleigh Mayer  New York, June 4, 2007</p>
      </block>
